{"lastModified":1760612171987,"uri":"c::8164602117::vessel::d5cbab83-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Gulet","Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nSmart Spirit is one of the safest and most beautifully designed gulets sailing the Adriatic. With four exquisite en-suite cabins, and a masterful chef, she is the ideal vessel for up to 8 guests.\n\nSmart Spirit is one of the very few RINA certified vessels of its type. She has previously proven herself by gracefull traversing the Mediterranean and even the Atlantic, but has found home in the calm Croatian waters of the Adriatic.","blueprint":{"name":"SMART SPIRIT","images":["/media/media::image::c::8164602117::vessel::d5cbab83-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::5729dcc0-b0c2-11ef-9e56-659a891383d1/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8164602117::vessel::d5cbab83-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::5741aa80-b0c2-11ef-9e56-659a891383d1/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8164602117::vessel::d5cbab83-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::5769cbf0-b0c2-11ef-9e56-659a891383d1/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8164602117::vessel::d5cbab83-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::576cb220-b0c2-11ef-9e56-659a891383d1/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8164602117::vessel::d5cbab83-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::5766beb0-b0c2-11ef-846f-2fed4692207c/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8164602117::vessel::d5cbab83-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::5762a000-b0c2-11ef-9e56-659a891383d1/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8164602117::vessel::d5cbab83-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::574fdb50-b0c2-11ef-9e56-659a891383d1/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8164602117::vessel::d5cbab83-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::57675af0-b0c2-11ef-9e56-659a891383d1/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8164602117::vessel::d5cbab83-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::57633c40-b0c2-11ef-9e56-659a891383d1/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8164602117::vessel::d5cbab8